Introducing Joss Stone [stylised as Introducing... Joss Stone] is the third studio album
by English singer and songwriter Joss Stone, released on 9 March 2007 by Virgin Records.
Stone began writing the album in April 2006 in Barbados, before meeting up with producer
Raphael Saadiq in the Bahamas to record the songs. Introducing Joss Stone also features
guest vocal appearances by rapper Common and singer Lauryn Hill.
